sql: SELECT d.Team, d.Team FROM technician AS d ORDER BY d.Team DESC
SELECT name, name FROM repair WHERE  repair_ID >= 8

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT repair_assignment.Machine_ID), value_points, technician_id FROM repair_assignment JOIN machine ON repair_assignment.Machine_ID = machine.Machine_ID WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM repair_assignment WHERE  repair_ID > 31 AND machine.Machine_ID = Machine_ID)

SELECT AVG(repair_assignment.repair_ID), repair_assignment.repair_ID FROM repair JOIN repair_assignment ON repair.repair_ID = repair_assignment.repair_ID GROUP BY repair_assignment.repair_ID ORDER BY repair_assignment.repair_ID ASC

SELECT technician.technician_id FROM technician JOIN technician AS o ON technician.technician_id = o.technician_id WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM repair_assignment WHERE technician.technician_id = technician_id) LIMIT 4

SELECT COUNT(repair_assignment.technician_id), Machine_ID FROM technician JOIN repair_assignment ON repair_assignment.technician_id = technician.technician_id WHERE  technician.technician_id != 89 GROUP BY Machine_ID
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT o.Starting_Year), o.Age FROM technician AS o WHERE  o.Starting_Year >= 3
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT i.repair_ID), i.Machine_ID FROM repair_assignment AS i WHERE  i.repair_ID < 74 GROUP BY i.Machine_ID ORDER BY i.Machine_ID ASC

SELECT SUM(repair_ID), Machine_ID FROM technician JOIN repair_assignment ON repair_assignment.technician_id = technician.technician_id WHERE Starting_Year BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  Machine_ID != 55 LIMIT 9

SELECT AVG(repair_assignment.Machine_ID), machine.Team FROM technician JOIN repair_assignment JOIN machine ON repair_assignment.Machine_ID = machine.Machine_ID AND repair_assignment.technician_id = technician.technician_id WHERE  value_points > 84 ORDER BY machine.Team ASC

SELECT quality_rank, Machine_series FROM repair_assignment JOIN machine ON repair_assignment.Machine_ID = machine.Machine_ID WHERE Making_Year BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  quality_rank > 34 GROUP BY Machine_series HAVING COUNT(machine.Machine_ID) = 11 LIMIT 10
SELECT COUNT(s.repair_ID), s.repair_ID FROM repair AS s WHERE  s.repair_ID < 95 LIMIT 4

SELECT Launch_Date FROM technician JOIN repair JOIN repair_assignment JOIN machine ON repair_assignment.Machine_ID = machine.Machine_ID AND repair_assignment.technician_id = technician.technician_id AND repair.repair_ID = repair_assignment.repair_ID WHERE  repair_assignment.technician_id < 12 LIMIT 7
SELECT Notes, Notes, Launch_Date FROM repair WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM repair_assignment WHERE  Machine_ID > 59 AND repair.repair_ID = repair_ID)

SELECT name FROM repair JOIN repair_assignment ON repair.repair_ID = repair_assignment.repair_ID WHERE Machine_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM repair WHERE repair_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND repair_assignment.technician_id = repair_ID) ORDER BY name ASC

SELECT machine.Machine_series, a.Making_Year FROM machine JOIN machine AS a ON machine.Machine_ID = a.Machine_ID WHERE a.quality_rank BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Machine_series <= (SELECT SUM(Machine_series) FROM machine AS n WHERE n.quality_rank BETWEEN 1 AND 10 LIMIT 7) GROUP BY a.Making_Year
SELECT value_points, Team FROM machine WHERE  value_points < 63 GROUP BY Team
SELECT COUNT(repair_ID), technician.technician_id FROM technician JOIN repair_assignment ON repair_assignment.technician_id = technician.technician_id WHERE  repair_ID <= 94
SELECT COUNT(technician.Age), technician.Team FROM technician JOIN technician AS s ON technician.technician_id = s.technician_id WHERE  technician.Age = 18 ORDER BY technician.Team ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT Starting_Year FROM technician WHERE technician_id IN (SELECT technician_id FROM repair_assignment WHERE  technician_id < 48) ORDER BY Starting_Year ASC LIMIT 10

SELECT Launch_Date, repair_assignment.Machine_ID FROM technician JOIN repair JOIN repair_assignment JOIN machine ON repair_assignment.Machine_ID = machine.Machine_ID AND repair_assignment.technician_id = technician.technician_id AND repair.repair_ID = repair_assignment.repair_ID WHERE  Starting_Year <= 53 GROUP BY repair_assignment.Machine_ID HAVING AVG(Age) >= 17

SELECT technician_id FROM repair JOIN repair_assignment ON repair.repair_ID = repair_assignment.repair_ID WHERE Notes >= (SELECT MAX(Notes) FROM repair AS z WHERE  z.repair_ID > 95) ORDER BY technician_id DESC LIMIT 2
SELECT c.repair_ID, c.repair_ID FROM repair AS c WHERE c.repair_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND name NOT IN (SELECT name FROM repair AS c WHERE  c.repair_ID >= 39) ORDER BY c.repair_ID DESC

SELECT COUNT(repair_assignment.technician_id), COUNT(DISTINCT Name), repair_ID FROM technician JOIN repair_assignment ON repair_assignment.technician_id = technician.technician_id GROUP BY repair_ID HAVING MIN(repair_ID) < 1
SELECT machine.Machine_ID, machine.Machine_ID, machine.Machine_ID FROM repair_assignment JOIN machine ON repair_assignment.Machine_ID = machine.Machine_ID WHERE  machine.Machine_ID = 91

SELECT Starting_Year, Name FROM technician JOIN repair JOIN repair_assignment ON repair_assignment.technician_id = technician.technician_id AND repair.repair_ID = repair_assignment.repair_ID WHERE  repair.repair_ID < 18 GROUP BY Starting_Year

SELECT technician_id, Launch_Date, Class, repair_assignment.Machine_ID FROM repair JOIN repair_assignment JOIN machine ON repair_assignment.Machine_ID = machine.Machine_ID AND repair.repair_ID = repair_assignment.repair_ID GROUP BY repair_assignment.Machine_ID
SELECT AVG(r.technician_id), r.repair_ID FROM repair_assignment AS r WHERE  r.technician_id > 16
SELECT SUM(repair_assignment.repair_ID), MAX(repair.repair_ID) FROM repair JOIN repair_assignment ON repair.repair_ID = repair_assignment.repair_ID WHERE repair_assignment.repair_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10
SELECT f.Team, f.Team FROM technician AS f WHERE  f.technician_id < 29

SELECT Machine_ID, technician_id FROM repair JOIN repair_assignment ON repair.repair_ID = repair_assignment.repair_ID WHERE technician_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR Machine_ID NOT IN (SELECT Machine_ID FROM machine AS w WHERE  w.quality_rank > 75) LIMIT 8

SELECT j.Team, j.Team, j.Starting_Year FROM technician AS j WHERE technician_id IN (SELECT technician_id FROM technician AS j WHERE  j.technician_id != 30 LIMIT 1) GROUP BY j.Starting_Year HAVING MIN(j.technician_id) <= 23 ORDER BY j.Starting_Year DESC
SELECT COUNT(repair_ID), Launch_Date, name FROM repair WHERE repair_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY name HAVING MIN(repair_ID) > 90

SELECT AVG(Machine_ID), Launch_Date FROM repair JOIN repair_assignment ON repair.repair_ID = repair_assignment.repair_ID WHERE technician_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Notes IN (SELECT Notes FROM repair) LIMIT 5
